EV isolated method: After precipitation of exosomes with the ExoQuick Exosome Precipitation Solution (System Biosciences-SBI), they were analyzed using an electron microscope (FEI Quanta 250, Thermo Fisher Scientific, Eindhoven, the Netherlands), the Nano particle tracking analysis (NTA) (ZetaView PMX 110, Particle Metrix, Meerbusch, Germany), and Western blot analysis (for CD63) were used to characterize isolated exosomes.
